snippet: Frenchman Gael Monfils maintained his run of brilliant form when he nullified Milos Raonic's big serve to eliminate the local favorite from the Rogers Cup in Toronto on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Frenchman Gael Monfils maintained his run of brilliant form when he nullified Milos Raonic's big serve to eliminate the local favorite from the Rogers Cup in Toronto on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Monfils Beats Raonic in Toronto, Djokovic Wins
